title: RNA-seq of Montipora capitata: 6_1phf
design_description: Using 150-190 ng of total RNA, rRNA-depleted RNA-Seq libraries were prepared using the Zymo-Seq RiboFree Total RNA Library Kit (R3000) with 15 cycles of library amplification (98°C for 20 seconds, 60°C for 30 seconds, 72°C for 30 seconds). Library concentration and size was determined with an Agilent Tapestation 4200. The libraries were sequenced at the Oklahoma Medical Research Foundation NGS Core on an Illumina NovaSeq X Plus in a 2x150 bp configuration.
